  <brief_title>Use of Curcumin in the Lower Gastrointestinal Tract in Familial Adenomatous Polyposis Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Curcumin in the Lower Gastrointestinal Tract in Familial Adenomatous Polyposis (FAP) Patients</official_title>
